nt||fp|2|at|My tip to you all is that you should play the Dbl of a slam to ask for an unusual lead; not to increase the penalty, but to tell partner not to make his normal lead. Make sure before you double, if you get the lead you want, you have a chance of another trick somewhere to beat the contract.
